      <title>必和必拓将通过初步工资协议避免智利矿工罢工</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-12/bhp-reaches-preliminary-wage-agreement-at-chilean-copper-mine</link>
      <description><![CDATA[必和必拓集团与智利工会领导人达成了初步工资协议，这意味着该公司将避免在智利这座铜矿发生代价高昂的罢工，该铜矿约占全球电线金属供应量的 1%。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-12/bhp-reaches-preliminary-wage-agreement-at-chilean-copper-mine</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 12 Jun 2024 05:01:00 GMT</pubDate>
