      <title>顶级银行家称劳工税上调将迫使客户转向海外</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-12/labour-tax-threat-poses-risk-to-clients-says-panmure-liberum</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Bidhi Bhoma 是 Panmure Liberum 的副首席执行官，Panmure Liberum 是由 Liberum 和 Panmure Gordon 合并而成的投资银行。该公司拥有 200 多家上市公司客户，宣布交易时在英国和北美拥有约 280 名员工。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-12/labour-tax-threat-poses-risk-to-clients-says-panmure-liberum</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 12 Jun 2024 04:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>柔佛种植园和居林拟进行 2022 年以来马来西亚最大规模 IPO</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-12/johor-plantations-kulim-eye-biggest-malaysian-ipo-in-two-years</link>
      <description><![CDATA[马来西亚棕榈油生产商柔佛种植园集团有限公司 (Johor Plantations Group Bhd) 及其股东预计通过首次公开募股 (IPO) 筹集约 7.35 亿林吉特 (1.56 亿美元)，使该集团有望实现该国两年多来最大规模的上市。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-12/johor-plantations-kulim-eye-biggest-malaysian-ipo-in-two-years</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 12 Jun 2024 03:16:52 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
